{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"65d07542cb","title":"五绝·赞“密使一号”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f2764a02c2","index":0,"year":1950,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"65d07542cb"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"6230ceb373","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65d07542cb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"“密使一号”，指华东局情报部门插入在台湾国民党军队核心高层中的地下工作者——吴石将军。吴石（1894-1950），1949年8月15日，福州解放在即，蒋介石手询电招吴石速赴台湾，吴石赴台前，中共地下组织给他的代号为“密使一号”。吴石抵达台湾后，就任国民党国防部参谋次长。1950年6月10日，被频徒出卖在台北从容就义。临刑前望着大陆的方向说：“台湾大陆都是一家人，这是血脉民心。几十年后，我会回到故里的。”为了表彰吴石将军为祖国统一大业做出的特殊贡献，1973年周恩来总理力排众议，在毛泽东主席的支持下，由国务院追认吴石将军为革命烈士。"},{"id":"9b8b3dde89","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65d07542cb","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"惊涛，暗指地下工作者时时身处在一种惊涛骏浪般的险恶环境之中。孤岛，指台湾。"},{"id":"cb32ff0d3a","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65d07542cb","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"虎穴藏忠魂，赞扬打入敌人内部的吴石将军的一片赤胆忠心。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f48e8d44de","type":"title","text":"五绝·赞“密使一号”口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65d07542cb"},{"id":"6230ceb373","type":"subtitle","text":"惊涛拍孤岛以，","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65d07542cb"},{"id":"9b8b3dde89","type":"paragraph","text":"碧波映天晓。虎穴藏忠魂曙光迎来早。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65d07542cb"}],"page":{"id":"1f8f0e9d0f","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"65d07542cb","start":188,"end":188}}}},"__N_SSG":true}